text: Saidingliana Sailo (born 27 November 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Mizoram in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. He made his first-class debut for Mizoram in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 1 November 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mizoram in the 2018–19 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy on 21 February 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Mizoram cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
